.Sh DESCRIPTION
This is a deprecated version of the
.Fn sqlite3_soft_heap_limit64
interface.
This routine is provided for historical compatibility only.
All new applications should use the
.Fn sqlite3_soft_heap_limit64
interface rather than this one.
